Plain Transcription: Odo, tù bag bag bi o yi sun re, bi gbe lup man yin bi.
With Diacritics: odò to ba gbagbe orisun rẹ gbigbe lo ma ngbe

Plain Transcription: Okolopo, orishi-orishi, onje yoribamu parelo, nipataki la arin anwotombe ilunla.
With Diacritics: ọpọlọpọ oriṣiriṣi ounjẹ yorùbá nparẹ lọ nípàtàkì larin awọn to ngbe ìlú nla

Plain Transcription: Owe yorobane ki agba do to de iliaye adi enje, adi enbun.
With Diacritics: òwe yorùbá ni ki àgbàdo to de ilẹ aye adìyẹ njẹ adìyẹ nmu

Plain Transcription: Ne opo odun seyin i resi ki ishe onje ojojuman, shuk bonfun an wan omo i balode i resi bure di ati indome.
With Diacritics: ni ọpọ ọdun sẹhin irẹsi ki ṣe ounjẹ ojojumọ ṣugbọn fun awọn ọmọ igbalode irẹsi burẹdi ati indomie ti di

Plain Transcription: Ni toyeyi o pobi kogi ayi lati she unje yuba.
With Diacritics: nítorí èyí ọpọ òbí ko ri aye lati se ounjẹ yorùbá

Plain Transcription: I alenu niwi kwe okwo anwa, siyo wa loke o kwe unje yoroba la uge ju anwa, siyo wa ne ile lo batake.
With Diacritics: ìyàlẹnu ni wipe ọpọ awọn ti ówà lokeokun ngbe ounjẹ yorùbá larugẹ ju awọn ti ówà ni ilé lọ pàtàkì

Plain Transcription: O She She, bebi ino mwono mwono, ba She Dede, unja yu ba, yu ba yi store anwa o male She Oishi Oishi.
With Diacritics: oṣeṣe pe bi iná manamana ba ṣe dédé ounjẹ yorùbá yio gbayi si nítorí awọn òbì ma le se oriṣiriṣi
